text: Fantastic Opportunity to Rent This Stunning 3 Beds/2 Baths Residence With a 2 Car Attached Garage and Unfinished Basement! Available on May 1st! The video tour is available at the bottom of this ad. Welcome to this cozy house in the desirable Broadlands area in Broomfield, CO. This property offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms, a gorgeous kitchen with tall cabinets and top-notch appliances, and a spacious living room with a cozy gas fireplace. The primary bedroom suite provides a private retreat after a long day; it connects to a 5-piece primary bathroom with a large walk-in closet. A two-car attached garage connects to the laundry room and is convenient for the security of your vehicles. An unfinished basement is perfect for storage. The bedroom in the basement would need to remain locked. The outside patio is conveniently accessible from the living room and the kitchen, where you can grill, gather, entertain, or enjoy your morning coffee. Additional features include a washer and dryer in the unit, A/C, trash, and snow removal included in the rent, and the indoor activity center is within walkable distance. Don't miss out on this incredible property. Please reach out to us today to schedule a tour. Up to two pets are okay with an additional $300 pet deposit and $35 monthly pet rent regardless of 1 or 2 pets. No aggressive breeds, only full-grown animals (12 months+), please. text: This spacious 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom single-family home located at 9816 W 99th Place in Westminster, CO, offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, and convenience. With plenty of space for families, guests, or even a home office, the home features five generously sized bedrooms and 3.5 modern bathrooms, ensuring privacy and comfort for everyone. The open-concept living areas are bright and inviting, ideal for both relaxing and entertaining. The updated kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, plenty of counter space, and a cozy eat-in area. For additional living space, the finished basement offers versatile options, whether as a game room, media room, or extra living area. The spacious primary suite boasts a large walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. Offered by All County Denver Metro Property Management We do full background checks & are seeking qualified, long-term residents. To view our rental criteria please visit our website. Application Fee: $65.00 each. Security Deposit is due at lease signing. Once approved, a one-time non-refundable administration fee of $345 will apply. All residents will be enrolled in Resident Benefits Package (RBP) for $39.99/month which includes Resident Rewards, Credit Building, Identity Protection, HVAC air filter delivery (for applicable properties), Online Payment Portal, 24/7 Maintenance Coordination, Utility Concierge Service, Digital Inspections and much more! Contact your leasing agent for more information. Additional Information: Applicant has the right to provide the property manager with a Portable Tenant Screening Report (PTSR) that is not more than 30 days old, as defined in Section 38-12-902(2.5), Colorado Revised Statutes; and 2) if Applicant provided the property manager with a PTSR, the property manager is prohibited from a) charging Applicant a rental application fee; or b) charging Application a fee for the property manager to access or use the PTSR.
